         %span
         %h4 Setup Shop
         %p Sell products and/or subscriptions without writing any code at all.
      %div{:class=>"point wallet"}
         %span
         %h4  Digital Wallet
         %p Securely store your credit cards to use for purchases.
      %div{:class=>"point debit"}
